---
title: Honey Mustard Glazed Salmon with a crispy Walnut Panko Crust
description: Honey mustard deserves recognition beyond the salad bar. In this recipe, we're using it to glaze salmon before burying it in a crunchy walnut crust. With some fluffy couscous and snappy roasted broccoli on the side, this dish becomes a harmonious medley of contrasting flavors and textures, venturing from spicy to sweet to tender to crispy.
